Task: FEATURE_BRAND_SYSTEM_APEX_FOUNDATION

Objective:
Create and apply a complete visual brand foundation for the finance app based on the "Apex" direction:
- premium
- controlled
- dark-first
- Apple-like clarity
- subtle progression / life-OS feel
- no cheesy gaming aesthetic
- no literal fintech clichés
